social_posts.post_text: Me for @primadonnalingerie holiday shot by the lovely @myladalbesio 💓 #weareprimadonna

Turned 28 on Tuesday. 🥰 So wild to reflect on where I am in life and what it took to get here. Forever grateful for my family and my friends who make me feel so loved and supported for being exactly who I am. Excited to see what type of growth and experiences this next year of life will bring 💓💖💓 
Also, @thirth should have a cake business because look at this cake she made me 🥹
Nothing better than a lil dump ✨💖✨
Little bit of this, little bit of that ✨
My personality summed up in a few swipes 🥰💕
